MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 1445830689}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: f59adbd143ce55544832d73be67cb622, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: '::'
  textUI: {fileID: 1445830691}
  fullText: "Journal Entry \u2014 19XX\n\nAs I write this log, I draw nearer to the
    Moon\u2019s far side\u2014its hidden face, spoken of with a kind of reverence
    I now find difficult to share. I am told I am the first to witness its unseen
    majesty.\n\nAll systems remain nominal. Yet the cabin feels wrong, as though
    the air has thickened beyond reason, pressing gently against thought itself.\n\nThere
    is a sound in the walls\u2014subtle, deliberate, like something learning the
    shape of my ship from within.\n\nA persistent pressure builds behind my eyes.
    I tell myself it is nothing. I continue the orbit."
  typingSpeed: 0.02
